{"seo": [], "title": "Anthony Kituyi Mulisa", "cta_link": "entry::3374", "cta_text": "Back to Executive Management", "leadership": "executive-management", "member_car": null, "updated_by": 30, "footer_type": "footers/main_footer", "header_type": "headers/country", "member_club": null, "member_team": null, "bottom_bar_nav": null, "team_member_text": "<p>Anthony Kituyi Mulisa is the Group Director, Treasury at KCB Group Plc. He was appointed in March 2024. Anthony has over 28 years of banking experience having spent 23 years in large and middle-sized treasuries in various African markets.</p>

<p>He has served in several treasury roles within Barclays PLC, Absa Group including National Bank of Commerce in Tanzania. He has chaired the Financial Markets Sub-committee of the Kenya Bankers Association (KBA), is a member of the Nairobi Securities Exchange (NSE), Derivative Board Oversight Committee and continues to serve on other corporate boards in Kenya.</p>

<p>Anthony is a certified currency and fixed-income trader through the ACI-Financial Markets (France) and an associate member of the Chartered Institute of Bankers (AGIB, UK). He holds a BSc degree in Financial Services from the University of Manchester and an MBA from Manchester Business School.</p>", "designation_title": "Designation:", "member_text_title": "Education and Professional Background:", "team_member_image": "antony-kituyi.png", "appointment_date_title": "Appointment Date:", "member_appointment_date": "2024-03-01", "team_member_designation": "Group Director, Treasury"}
